===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[facetious]] or [[insult]]ing remark, a [[jeer]] or [[taunt]].
#: ''He flung subtle '''jibes''' at her until she couldn't bear to work with him any longer.''
# {{context|nautical|lang=en}} A manoeuver in which the [[stern]] of a sailing [[boat]] or [[ship]] crosses the [[wind]], typically resulting in the sudden sweep of the [[boom]] from one side of the sailboat to the other.

